    "Figure 3.11 shows the ChatGPT interface where the model is asked to generate a short email and it responds with an email template.",
    "As for training a model, the user can adopt few-shot learning (see Section 3.2.3), passing examples in the prompts, or fine-tune the model, as mentioned in Section 3.2.4",
